Note: Auto attacks, Ice Shard, and Icy Wind can critically strike. Glaceon's Critical-Hit rate increases at levels 5 and 9. At level 4, Glaceon gains 12.5% spell vamp (restores HP when dealing Special Attack damage). When on a team with four other eeveelutions, gains +1% basic attack speed.

Eevee

Evolves At 4

Run Away

Passive Ability

When Eevee would be affected by a hindrance, the hindrance is negated and becomes invincible for 1s. This Ability goes on cooldown after it’s triggered (70s cd).

Snow Cloak

Passive Ability

When Glaceon would be affected by a hindrance, the hindrance is negated. Glaceon then starts sneaking and becomes invincible for 0.5s. This Ability goes on cooldown after it’s triggered (70s cd) and is reset after respawning.

Attack

Auto Attack

Becomes a boosted attack with every third attack, dealing increased damage and giving Glaceon 2 ice crystals when the boosted attack hits. Ice crystals last 5s and the duration is refreshed upon gaining additional crystals. Glaceon can hold a maximum of 8 ice crystals at a time.

39% SpA + 4 x (Level - 1) + 70

44.85% SpA + 5 x (Level - 1) + 81

47% SpA + 5 x (Level - 1) + 90

Swift

Move 1

5.00s Buff

Creates 4 stars around the user. For a short time afterward, each time the user hits an enemy with a basic attack or boosted attack, one or two of the stars respectively will shoot out and deal additional damage to the target.

16% SpA + 6 x (Level - 1) + 110

Swift Upgrade Choices

Icicle Spear

5.00s Sure Hit

Glaceon launches all of its stored ice crystals in rapid succession at the designated enemy. If Glaceon has no ice crystals when this move is used, 2 ice crystals are instantly created and are launched. Launched ice crystals can hit enemies on the opposing team that are not the designated target of this move. The crystals shatter when they hit any enemy, dealing damage to all enemies in the area. Ice crystals launched by this move deal 5% increased damage each time they hit the same enemy (capped at 35%). When this move is used, Ice Shard's cooldown is reduced by 2s and Freeze Dry's cooldown is reduced by 2.5s. A maximum of 12 ice crystals may be launched.

37% SpA + 4 x (Level - 1) + 97

Each launched ice crystal also deals additional damage to enemies hit equal to 0.5% of their remaining HP.

Against Wild Pokémon: This additional damage is capped at 300.

Icy Wind

6.50s Dash

Jump a short distance in the designated direction; Glaceon's next auto attack within 5s gains increased range and launches all stored ice crystals at an enemy, dealing damage to them. Glaceon then regains the same number of ice crystals that were launched. If an enemy is hit by 4 or more ice crystals, their movement speed is decreased by 8% per shard (stacking up to 6 times) for 1s. If Glaceon has no ice crystals when this move is used, gain 2 ice crystals.

20% SpA + 2 x (Level - 1) + 35

Each launched ice crystal also deals additional damage to enemies hit equal to 1.5% of their remaining HP.

Against Wild Pokémon: This additional damage is capped at 300.

Tail Whip

Move 2

8.00s Sure Hit

Has the user wag its tail at an enemy, dealing damage and decreasing their Defense and Sp. Def by 30% for 2s, and movement speed by 20% for 1.5s. The next auto attack after using this move becomes a boosted attack.

61% SpA + 6 x (Level - 1) + 190

Tail Whip Upgrade Choices

Ice Shard

8.50s Buff

Glaceon gains an increase in movement speed by 40% for 1s while basic attack speed is increased by 60% for 2.5s. Basic attacks change into attacks that hurl chunks of ice for 2.5s. These chunks of ice deal damage to enemies they hit and decrease their movement speed by 30% for 1s. Each time a chunk of ice hits, Glaceon gains 2 ice crystals. If this move is used while launching crystals with Icicle Spear, or if this move is used after Icy Wind but before launching all crystals with the next auto attack, gain 2 ice crystals and increase Glaceon's movement speed by 50% for 0.5s.

52% SpA + 6 x (Level - 1) + 100

Increases basic attack speed further to 100% for 2.5s.

Freeze Dry

8.50s Ranged

Shoot out a freezing burst of air in a forward direction. This burst explodes upon hitting an enemy or after traveling a set distance; dealing damage to all enemies in the area. Upon hitting an enemy, increase Glaceon's Sp. Atk by 50% for 3s. For each enemy hit by the explosion, Glaceon gains 2 ice crystals. The explosion also leaves behind an ice zone which slows enemies that enter by 30% for 3s. If they remain in the ice zone for 2.5s, they become frozen for 0.6s.

71% SpA + 5 x (Level - 1) + 226

For each enemy hit by this move's explosions, Glaceon gains 1 additional ice crystal.

Glacial Stage

Unite Move

100s 90000 Area

Unlocks at level 8

Glaceon leaps up high, creating an ice zone in front of themself that deals damage to enemies in the area-of-effect. While Glaceon is in the ice zone, their movement speed is increased by 50% for 6s, and Glaceon gains 1 ice crystals every second while in the zone. The movement speed of enemies in the ice zone is decreased by 50% for 2s.

100% SpA + 7 x (Level - 1) + 320

Unite Buffs (6s duration):

30% Movement Speed, 35% Attack Speed, 20% Max HP Shield
